  "subject": "Modernize dependency management with Spring Boot",
  "commit_message": "Modernize dependency management with Spring Boot\n\nMigrate from individual Spring dependencies to Spring Boot starters\nand use Spring Boot BOM for central dependency management.\n\n- Centralize dependency versions with Spring Boot Dependencies BOM\n- Override versions for CVE fixes like Jackson Core\n- Replace individual Spring dependencies with Spring Boot starters\n- Remove Spring Boot 4 \"classic\" starters (removes many dependencies)\n- Replace Spring Cloud Kubernetes with direct kubernetes client\n- Clean up unused maven profiles and plugin configs\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5552\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I8883f16c2083544fb16ec1e0f126def649183ba6\n",
